I just heard that Santa Clara University didn’t let freshmen defer because of the coronavirus.

All I can say is that they better not except a single dollar from them when it comes time to ask for alumni donations.

@SantaClaraUniv

@AdmiSadakKa I enjoy riling them up without using four letter words (something they do.)

Remember the despicable Rohit Chopra of @SantaClaraUniv ? He hated being called a math failure, so much so that his rants were deleted by Twitter weeks before he got suspended permanently.

Good times.
